    "type": "message",
    "text": "Hello coders of the future... I'm the organizer of the Strange Loop conference and we have a long interest in exploring the future of programming languages, having hosted the Emerging Languages conference in 2012 and 2013 and Future of Programming in 2015 and lots of other talks as well. We are planning for an in-person conference Sep 30-Oct 2 (1st day preconf, 2 day conf) in St. Louis. If you're interested in submitting something, our CFP is open now until May 5th. <https://thestrangeloop.com/cfp.html>",
